# Keep build images lean: the builder only needs poms + src for common/, engine/ and the one
# service. Everything below is either huge (Berka data, ~86 MB), rebuilt inside the image
# (target/), or irrelevant to the build (VCS, docs, IDE).
**/target/
data/
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.project
.settings/
.classpath
bin/
*.md
*.iml
.idea/
.vscode/
*.workflow.js
qa/
docs/
docker-compose.yml
.dockerignore
Dockerfile
**/Dockerfile
